<h1>Resume Verification &amp; Dynamic CV Builder</h1>
<h2>Detailed Product Requirements Document (PRD)</h2>
<p><b>Version:</b> 1.0<br/>
<b>Date:</b> 21 April 2026<br/>
<b>Prepared for:</b> Program Team / Placement Operations</p>

<h2>1. Product Overview</h2>
<p>This product enables students to submit resume points with proof, allows the program team to verify and govern claim quality, detects risky semantic edits, and generates role-specific CVs from approved content.</p>

<h3>1.1 Primary Goals</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Asynchronous submission and verification workflow</li>
  <li>Dynamic CV generation from verified points</li>
  <li>Risk assessment for semantic/contextual misrepresentation</li>
  <li>Deadline enforcement for submission and edit control</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Roles and Permissions</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Role</th><th>Capabilities</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Student</td><td>Create/edit points, upload proofs, submit/re-submit, build CV variants from approved points, download PDF.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Program Team</td><td>Search students, review points, approve/flag/reject, set deadlines, monitor risk, export reports.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Admin (optional)</td><td>Manage templates, categories, system configuration, role policies, and analytics exports.</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>3. End-to-End Workflow</h2>
<p><b>Point lifecycle:</b> Draft -&gt; Submitted -&gt; Under Review -&gt; Approved / Flagged / Rejected -&gt; Revised -&gt; Final Approved</p>
<ol>
  <li>Student adds point and proof(s).</li>
  <li>Student submits point for verification.</li>
  <li>Risk engine computes score and explanation.</li>
  <li>Program team reviews and decides.</li>
  <li>Student receives comments and revises (if allowed).</li>
  <li>Approved points become available in CV builder.</li>
</ol>

<h2>4. Feature Specification</h2>
<h3>4.1 Student Module</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Dashboard with status counts, deadlines, recent feedback.</li>
  <li>Point repository with categories and filters.</li>
  <li>Proof upload (PDF/JPG/PNG/DOCX + links).</li>
  <li>Revision history and reviewer comments.</li>
  <li>CV builder with templates, point selection, ordering, PDF export.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4.2 Program Team Module</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Main dashboard shows all students in a batch with search and filters.</li>
  <li>Click student to open full profile and status analytics.</li>
  <li>Tabs for all pointers: Pending, Approved, Rejected, Red Flagged.</li>
  <li>Point-level review with proof panel and AI risk reason.</li>
  <li>Deadline manager (submission, edit cutoff, final verification).</li>
</ul>

