<h2>6. Risk Assessment Logic</h2>
<h3>6.1 Objective</h3>
<p>Identify whether a submitted or edited point changes factual meaning, role level, scope, or impact beyond verified evidence.</p>

<h3>6.2 Scoring Model (0-100)</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Signal</th><th>Example</th><th>Score Impact</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Responsibility escalation</td><td>"assisted" → "led"</td><td>+30 to +45</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Scope inflation</td><td>"module" → "platform"</td><td>+20 to +35</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Metric inflation</td><td>New % added without proof</td><td>+25 to +40</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Semantic drift</td><td>Low similarity with original point</td><td>+20 to +35</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Proof mismatch</td><td>Strong claim, weak evidence</td><td>+20 to +25</td></tr>
</table>
<p><b>Risk bands:</b> Low (0-29), Medium (30-64), High (65+)</p>

<h3>6.3 Hard Flag Conditions</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Contributor-to-owner claim change without evidence</li>
  <li>Quantitative claim added without traceable proof</li>
  <li>Team leadership claim appears newly without historical support</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. API Outline</h2>
<ul>
  <li>POST /api/points</li>
  <li>PATCH /api/points/:id</li>
  <li>POST /api/points/:id/submit</li>
  <li>GET /api/batches/:id/students-summary</li>
  <li>GET /api/students/:id/profile</li>
  <li>POST /api/verification/:pointId/approve</li>
  <li>POST /api/verification/:pointId/flag</li>
  <li>POST /api/verification/:pointId/reject</li>
  <li>POST /api/cv-builder/generate</li>
  <li>POST /api/deadlines</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Data Model (Conceptual)</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Students, Batches, Points, PointVersions, Proofs</li>
  <li>Verifications, Comments, Deadlines</li>
  <li>CVVariants, Templates, AuditLogs</li>
</ul>

<h2>9. Deadline Rules</h2>
<ul>
  <li>After submission deadline: no new submissions.</li>
  <li>After edit cutoff: no student edits/resubmissions.</li>
  <li>After final verification deadline: reviewer actions restricted (policy-based).</li>
</ul>

<h2>10. MVP Delivery Plan (8 Weeks)</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Week</th><th>Focus</th></tr>
  <tr><td>1-2</td><td>Authentication, roles, base data models</td></tr>
  <tr><td>3-4</td><td>Point CRUD, proof uploads, submission flow</td></tr>
  <tr><td>5-6</td><td>Verification queue, risk engine v1, comments</td></tr>
  <tr><td>7</td><td>CV builder, templates, PDF generation</td></tr>
  <tr><td>8</td><td>QA, deadline policies, reporting and hardening</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>11. Acceptance Criteria (Key)</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Program team can search and open any student profile from dashboard.</li>
  <li>Each profile shows pending/approved/rejected/red-flagged counts.</li>
  <li>Reviewers can approve/flag/reject with comments.</li>
  <li>Risk engine returns score + explanation for each submitted point.</li>
  <li>Students can generate PDF CVs from approved points only.</li>
  <li>Editing and submission lock correctly after deadlines.</li>
</ol>

<p><b>End of Document</b></p>
